                        <p>When designing an online store, a lot of focus goes into the homepage—after all, it’s the first thing visitors see when they arrive. But the real goal of any ecommerce website is sales, and there’s no way you’ll achieve that without stellar product pages</p>
                        <p>Effective product pages immediately convey the value of a featured product. They show potential customers what a product looks like, tell them what it feels like, and make them believe it’s something they absolutely need to own.</p>
                        <p>The product page includes several key elements to help shoppers decide if they want to buy:</p>
                    </div>

                    <ul class="single-work-product__list _list">
