                        <li>Shipping policy. Intelligent calculation of delivery time based on the product and buyer location</li>
                        <li>Additional sales. Standard opportunity to increase the check for retail</li>
                        <li>Cheaper together. Multipurpose promotional tool. It is convenient to choose a set for yourself</li>
                        <li>Extended feedback. Stars, voting, answers, hierarchy</li>
                    </ul>

                    <p>Scroll down, though, and a more robust product discovery experience awaits. Graphics that highlight the features, benefits, and materials of each product along with user-generated content in the form of videos give you a deeper dive. </p>
